channel.description:
http://rune4death.biz/
Yes I posted before but the reason for re-posting is because we just got rid of some staff who really didn't deserve it,
We have a really good eco, a lot more updates coming, all bosses work, nex,kbd and qbd!! lots more!
We have a full pking tab,training tab that gets updated, skiller tab, bossing tab and lots more.
Dominion tower works, we have a zombie minigame, Clan wars, soul wars, construction works, lunar,curses,ancients and lots more!
We will be looking for more staff soon as well as we got rid of some staff who never deserved it, don't ask me how they got it but they are gone now, So we will be looking for active players and who know a lot about the server or can always try the best to answer a question a player has, Please try it out I promise you will love the server!
Sorry I can't put pictures up as my computer won't screen shot :(.
